up the counternarcotics center with representatives from dea fbi 
customs coast guard and other federal agencies with a mission to 
advise policymakers on how to fight drug trafficking 
the proliferation of coordinators has some involved in the 
drug enforcement efforts disgusted although none will go on the 
record with their objections 
