a bomb exploded at a restaurant in the 
drug trafficking center of medellin and police said today that four 
people were injured including two american journalists 
no one immediately claimed responsibility for the blast tuesday 
night but drug lords recently declared war on the government after 
it began cracking down on the traffickers for a string of bombings 
and assassinations 
