asked 
yes sir bakker responded quietly 
asked if he was able to assist his lawyers bakker said im 
very tired but i believe i can 
his wife tammy said as she left court this should not be 
allowed in the united states of america 
potter did not immediately rule on a defense request for a 
mistrial but said he expected the trial to resume at 2 pm 
bakker who resigned from the ptl ministry in 1987 in a sex and 
money scandal went on trial aug 28 on conspiracy and fraud 
