mutual funds which he called the loose cannon of the financial 
system 
it is a source of worry he said ill guarantee you that 
nine out of 10 people that have their money in those mutual money 
markets uninsured dont know that theyre not insured that 
has to be looked at 
commercial banks hold about 24 trillion in deposits followed 
by sampls with 960 billion money market mutual funds with 330 
billion and credit unions with 195 billion all except mutual funds 
are federally insured 
