integration products for clients the computer maker is price 
waterhouses largest audit client 
ibm is a big question bowman said there are definite 
conflicts of interest that have to be resolved before they can do a 
merger 
federal securities and exchange commission rules bar an 
accounting firm from participating in joint ventures with one of its 
audit clients because of possible conflicts of interest 
