this restructuring recognizes a need to simplify and streamline 
domestic oil and gas operations while at the same time generating 
additional cash to sustain or improve capital programs for 
exploration and development david hentschel chairman and chief 
executive officer of the tulsabased company said tuesday 
occidental oil amp gas corp including oxy usa is a subsidiary of 
occidental petroleum corp based in los angeles 
