the companys headquarters in tulsa just before noon employees said 
verle mccoy manager of financial accounting for occidental oil amp 
gas said employees had been hearing layoff rumors since may 
occidental oil amp gas employs about 1750 in tulsa and about 4500 
each in its international and domestic operations 
the company is closing its exploration operations in tulsa as 
