66 percent stake in midway revealed the additional stock 
accumulation in a filing with the securities and exchange commission 
in its original sec filing aug 7 the pittsburghbased company 
said it had bought midway shares for investment and to acquire a 
significant equity interest adding that it may also consider 
seeking to acquire control of midway 
ampco spokesman marshall berkman said the companys purpose in 
acquiring the additional shares was the same as in its original 
filing 
